data.description: Space, space, and more space in this Texas style, Texas sized home in the highly desirable Parkside at Mayfield Ranch community.  The first of many flexible lifestyle spaces starts with an Office with French Door to suit work from home needs.   A closet makes it possible to turn in to guest room, hobby room, anything you want room.  Next up is a Formal Dining for your next life celebration.   The Gourmet Kitchen will make prepping for that celebration a breeze with center island, granite countertops, and stainless appliances.  Casual Dining is great for breakfast bites or laying out a buffet.   Two story windows let light flood into the spacious Family Room.  Well appointed Primary Suite with full bath featuring separate vanities, soaking tub, and walk-in shower.  Upstairs you'll find room for large and growing families.  A gameroom and four secondary bedrooms provide space for everyone or use one of the bedrooms for your own yoga space.  Outdoor lifestyle needs are met with a covered patio and a separate terraced area with low maintenance turf.  A host of community amenities including park and pool and community trails that lead to nearby Southwest Williamson County Regional Park.  Leander ISD and onsite elementary.
